Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是第一次见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这次要拍的知道是什么吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,知道是 关于屁股的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 屁股是主题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然以前可能也做过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这次 还是想拍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 感觉屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是我 不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,直接这样隔着裤子摸也可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一提 你觉得自己的屁股如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 竟然脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是很喜欢 从学生时代开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是感觉 有点太突出了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是有一点突出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也不是很差把?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下半身比较内敛的人更多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是觉得rio很瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过屁股的肉感很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被玩弄的敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这也是采访哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得自己拍过的主题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个总集是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有了解过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,应该看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回忆以前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄现场有没有什么印象深刻的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,重新回想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 被玩弄的好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 现场的回忆是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是今年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今年其实有很多是我第一次拍的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,比如吃饭时做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在雨中做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个总集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还拍过一次回忆篇那种的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从小学开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个真的是有点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 后面注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以前的经历也很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,演唱会很辛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的是 托您的福 能够举办演出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,彩排什么的 很辛苦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,彩排?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 叁十个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起跟上节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对每个人来说都很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股有点不妙啊 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点被玩弄的很紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的已经是很紧张的状态了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧张?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在真的很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的 不要这样对我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真的很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对你做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对你自己来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,口交 喜欢还是讨厌?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,口交吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,口交的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实没有怎么被别人舔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 这也不是你要道歉的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶? 要干吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是要 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样被ロ没试过吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一般自己是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在看的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那不如就放开一点享受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以坐上去哦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样口交不舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 也不是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是那种很喜欢口交的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种看着自己被口的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会完全没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有到讨厌的地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那里肯定很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请问好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来还可以这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,rio应该是第一次这样看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手指插进去会怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手指插进去的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会觉得有点害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还要这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我很喜欢的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说屁股喜欢被玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会觉得很性奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 被对方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉被侵犯的那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今年其实也拍了很多主题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么最喜欢的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样玩弄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 今年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 我没办法思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那说一下去年出演电影的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 确实 托您的福 出演了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一样吧 拍摄现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然知道是很不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有点紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你又怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次看着自己被玩弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧 大家?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过能看到不是更好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢 会很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,后面全都张开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然本来就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于去年的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么有趣的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能随便说一个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到了变态的的士司机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,变态司机?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 碰到过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多问一句 你没出事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用玩具插进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能不同意对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能继续讲刚才的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我说可以和我做爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个变态司机吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 差不多两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,直接就说这个了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,问了我喜欢的类型之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就说起和那种人做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一直说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,果然男人和女人差别是很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我说 确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实到这里就过了一个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在故意绕圈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我都已经结账了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他是不让你下车?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他就接着说等一下能不能和我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他想直接把你拐走是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就感觉去家里也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就在车上 或者酒店里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以的这种氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他是发现了你是rio吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他还问了我叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我说我是rio
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 原来是女优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么两个女优我很喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后有一个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不能这么深
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你又怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要潮吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 因为现在还在采访
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 果然不能在这种场合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你平时一般会去哪里购物呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,平时的话 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,新宿之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的会去新宿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 下面的感觉实在太强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 不会暴露吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实被别人搭讪过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么搭话的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以具体说一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别人怎么向你搭讪的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,详细是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种擦肩而过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 震动可以选择强吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你对这个很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 但是我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一直盯着看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 感觉不是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为从来没这样看过自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在路上被人问是不是女优 你怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我会说 对 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果想和你拍照呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被要求拍照的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还是会拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一直和别人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于去年印象深刻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去年不是出演了电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在抱歉 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是要射精了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都射在我屁股上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也感觉要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要出来了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太强烈了 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喷出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 采访就到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那宣传片的片头 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量性感一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要尽量性感是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 毕竟是一个作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我今年也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就是正片了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和我亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点互相舔舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢像这样被舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到处 都想被你舔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也想被舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以逃避哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都立起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢你这种敏感的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡也立起来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,变得很下流了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这样硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以立起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没感受到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 闻到下流的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然擅自开始舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在多舔几下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小屄都变得有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的小屄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是你最喜欢的对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是还不可以玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要慢慢的来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是下流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想直接舔那里了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 很想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,rio可爱的小屄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很想舔是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,超级想舔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,首先的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要让我屁股舒服才可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很想看小屄对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能让我很舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我就帮你舔鸡鸡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.03,0:24:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点用力吸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 多吸一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:24:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:25:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,会上瘾的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.03,0:25:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦 努力吸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.03,0:25:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很性奋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.03,0:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.03,0:25:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要伸进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.03,0:25:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好舔等下才能帮你爽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.03,0:25:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 鸡鸡也立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.03,0:25:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.03,0:26:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.03,0:26:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.03,0:26:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.03,0:26:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.03,0:26:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你好好舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.03,0:26:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好和我一起做很下流的事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.03,0:26:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.03,0:27:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.03,0:27:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.03,0:27:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 快吸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.03,0:27:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很痛苦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.03,0:27:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让你很不舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.03,0:27:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,更多
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.03,0:27:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想继续
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.03,0:27:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不要这么着急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.03,0:27:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.03,0:28:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.03,0:28:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 很想喝吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.03,0:28:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.03,0:28:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.03,0:28:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个地方 太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.03,0:28:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.03,0:28:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看鸡鸡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.03,0:29:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 硬硬的 还在动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.03,0:29:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以哦 要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.03,0:29:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不准逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是要这样吸才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.03,0:30:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.03,0:30:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个姿势感觉很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.03,0:30:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.03,0:30:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.03,0:31:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.03,0:31:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.03,0:31:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了 要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可以射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.03,0:31:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不准射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多羞羞的事没做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.03,0:31:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮我张开吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.03,0:31:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愿意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.03,0:32:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.03,0:32:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.03,0:32:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快要进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.03,0:32:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很想进去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.03,0:32:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.03,0:32:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.03,0:33:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这种感觉好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.03,0:33:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全插进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.03,0:33:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.03,0:33:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.03,0:33:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好像一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.03,0:33:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.03,0:34:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.03,0:34:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.03,0:34:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还不准你射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.03,0:34:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.03,0:34:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不会累
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.03,0:34:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.03,0:35:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.03,0:35:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是太爽了 不想停了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.03,0:35:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里 就是那里 太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.03,0:35:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.03,0:35:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.03,0:35:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.03,0:36:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡进去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.03,0:36:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 又滑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.03,0:36:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.03,0:36:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.03,0:36:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.03,0:36:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.03,0:36:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.03,0:36:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,rio的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.03,0:36:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.03,0:36:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 小屄太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.03,0:37:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还不可以射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.03,0:37:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想感受高潮吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很想
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.03,0:38:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.03,0:38:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.03,0:38:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.03,0:38:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的感受也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.03,0:38:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡被紧紧的包住了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.03,0:38:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以夹得很紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.03,0:39:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.03,0:39:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以慢一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.03,0:39:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 会射出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.03,0:39:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.03,0:39:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.03,0:39:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.03,0:39:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.03,0:39:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.03,0:39:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.03,0:39:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.03,0:40:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我来动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.03,0:40:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.03,0:40:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点让我爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.03,0:41:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.03,0:41:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.03,0:41:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请一定要和我一起高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.03,0:41:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要忍到顶点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.03,0:42:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡又进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.03,0:42:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.03,0:42:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.03,0:42:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.03,0:42:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.03,0:43:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.03,0:43:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.03,0:43:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.03,0:43:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.03,0:43:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.03,0:44:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.03,0:44:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.03,0:44:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.03,0:44:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.03,0:44:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.03,0:44:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也快要射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.03,0:44:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.03,0:44:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想射在屁股上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.03,0:44:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.03,0:45:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要在我的屁股上 射很多精液哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.03,0:45:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.03,0:45:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,更快
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.03,0:46:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要插到最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.03,0:46:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.03,0:46:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.03,0:47:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.03,0:47:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.03,0:47:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.03,0:47:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.03,0:47:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想射了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.03,0:47:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想射出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.03,0:48:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,贴紧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.03,0:48:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,紧紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.03,0:48:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡太棒了 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.03,0:49:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽 好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.03,0:49:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,贴得好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.03,0:49:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一起高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.03,0:49:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.03,0:50:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.03,0:50:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要 全部吸光咯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.03,0:51:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.03,0:51:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 真的好安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.03,0:52:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢做一些色情的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.03,0:52:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是色鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.03,0:53:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.03,0:54:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,各种地方都舔舔看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.03,0:54:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,勃起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.03,0:55:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是下流的鸡鸡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.03,0:55:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.03,0:55:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.03,0:55:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡已经硬的不行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.03,0:55:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等下再慢慢感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.03,0:56:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.03,0:56:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是已经很性奋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.03,0:56:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想到小屄就会这样勃起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.03,0:56:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.03,0:57:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.03,0:58:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鸡鸡真的很硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.03,0:58:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.03,0:58:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.03,0:58:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,迫不及待的想插入了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.03,0:59:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很难受吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.03,0:59:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你鸡鸡变得更硬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.03,0:59:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小屄可以随便舔哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.03,1:00:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.03,1:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.03,1:00:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这声音听起来好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.03,1:00:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.03,1:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 慢慢的吸
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.03,1:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.03,1:01:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.03,1:01:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那里 吸
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.03,1:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,贴近我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.03,1:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再近一点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.03,1:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把吸过小屄的口水给我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.03,1:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的汁液吸到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.03,1:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,玩点别的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.03,1:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还不可以开始哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.03,1:02:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是我要动
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.03,1:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以自己来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.03,1:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,rio的屁股怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.03,1:03:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.03,1:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小屄还没有感受过对吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.03,1:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能听到小屄发出的声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.03,1:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 小屄都流水了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.03,1:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好像真的插入了一样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.03,1:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太舒服了 不想停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.03,1:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的屁股 可以再快一点吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.03,1:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小屄好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.03,1:04:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.03,1:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真的和插入一样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.03,1:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.03,1:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能感受到鸡鸡哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.03,1:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下面变得滑溜溜的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.03,1:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿好湿哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.03,1:05:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.03,1:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的小屄 已经感受到了哦
